Tutorial ⬇️
• Use those sound
• Use a pretty filter for the first few seconds (the expectation)
• Use a silly filter for the end (the reality)

Super simple! Just make sure you relate it to your niche!!

👗 How you look in your bathroom mirror VS. How you look on camera
